{
  "texts": [
    "The gathering and possible management of Ae.",
    "tauschii for food, or its co-cultivation as a weed over an extended period might have resulted in mixing of Ae.",
    "tauschii populations with different geographical origins, leading to an increase of admixed accessions close to human settlements.",
    "Such an admixed Ae.",
    "tauschii population might have later given rise to the bread wheat D genome."
  ]
}